
				         OOtemplate Oriented Object Template

  What is it?
  -----------

	OOTemplate is a template engine write in PHP5. Originally
	inspired by Django Template most popular template engine write
	in Python.
	Actually this project in a developement and it is not conseilled to use
	OOTemplate for a production mode.

  Documentation
  -------------

  The documentation available of this release is included in 
	HTML format in the doc/ directory. 

  Installation
  ------------

  Please see the file called INSTALL.

